Verbatim mirrors of third-party works
-------------------------------------

Material under content/docs-mirror/ that mirrors government edicts (statutes,
ordinances, agency-authored design manuals) is in the public domain in the
United States and is not subject to the CC BY-SA license. Each such page
identifies its source and verification date.

This repository contains no verbatim copies of copyrighted third-party works
(Autodesk Civil 3D Help, AASHTO publications, ALTA/NSPS standards, or paid
manuals). References to those works are by citation only. Licensed mirrors,
where they exist, live in a separate private store accessible only to
authorized users of the companion application.

